.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The course aims at teaching practical knowledge of techniques and methods used at sewing all important folk costumes, practical knowledge of materials, and application  of those skills in making clothes.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon passing the subject, the student: - will be conversant with the techniques used for flaxen folk costume and sequence of the steps; - will be able to select suitable materials, patterns, decoration methods;  - will be able to use the acquired techniques in making the basic components of folk costume sets.
